sequenceDiagram
  participant B as Browser (web/)
  participant A as server/app.py (Flask :5005)
  participant V as vbpoc (Voicebox :17493)
  participant FS as stories/ + voices_list.txt

  B->>A: GET /api/voices
  A->>V: getprofiles() (+ voices.reconcile vs voices_list.txt)
  A-->>B: matched / reference_only / voicebox_only
  B->>A: GET /api/stories  (folders with scripts, validate_book counts)
  B->>A: GET /api/story/:name  (speakers across scripts + current voices)
  B->>A: POST /api/preview {voice,text}
  A->>V: _generate_to_wav  →  WAV bytes
  A-->>B: audio/wav  (played in an audio element)
  B->>A: POST /api/story/:name {assignments}
  A->>FS: mapping_io.write_assignments (format-safe, in place)
  Note over B,FS: voices_list.txt edits export as a browser download
